Package: cryoCompare
Type: Package
Title: cryoCompare: comparisons for cryo-ET segmentation and denoising algorithms
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jeremy", "Chan",
      email = "jeremych.chan@mail.utoronto.ca",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: cryoCompare provides tools to compare cryo-electron tomography 
  (cryoET) datasets through segmentation and denoising algorithms in a 
  unified workflow. The package streamlines processing andvisualization, 
  allowing users to assess and visualize algorithm performance on real 
  tomographic data.
